    <item>
      <title>特朗普就任总统前，中国科技股对冲风险降低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/china-tech-stock-hedges-cheapen-before-trump-becomes-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普即将开始第二任期，全球投资者正准备迎接贸易政策的重大变化。他们关注的一个领域是中国科技，而投资者的情绪是：观望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/china-tech-stock-hedges-cheapen-before-trump-becomes-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GMT 称比亚迪的供应链融资掩盖了不断膨胀的债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/byd-s-supply-chain-financing-masks-ballooning-debt-gmt-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据香港 GMT Research 的计算，比亚迪股份有限公司对营运资金融资的依赖掩盖了这家中国电动汽车巨头不断飙升的债务水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/byd-s-supply-chain-financing-masks-ballooning-debt-gmt-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反向押注出现，美联储下一步举措是加息，而不是降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/contrarian-bet-emerges-that-next-fed-move-is-higher-not-lower</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这充其量只是一个设想，但却在一群坚定的债券交易员中浮现出来——美联储下一步的利率举措将是上调，而不是下调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/contrarian-bet-emerges-that-next-fed-move-is-higher-not-lower</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚天然气罐车爆炸死亡人数上升至 86 人，55 人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-19/urgent-nigerian-gasoline-tanker-explosion-death-toll-rises-to-86-with-55-others-injured</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿布贾，尼日利亚（美联社）——尼日利亚紧急救援机构周日表示，尼日利亚中北部一辆汽油罐车爆炸造成的死亡人数已上升至 86 人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-19/urgent-nigerian-gasoline-tanker-explosion-death-toll-rises-to-86-with-55-others-injured</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 19:52:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>弗里兰在加拿大竞选中表示，她可以打败特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/freeland-opens-canada-leadership-campaign-with-message-she-can-fight-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰周日正式启动竞选加拿大总理的竞选活动，她告诉支持者，她是与美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普竞争的最佳候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/freeland-opens-canada-leadership-campaign-with-message-she-can-fight-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 19:24:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>航空业的排放惯性正在困扰新西兰的门户</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/aviation-s-emissions-inertia-is-troubling-new-zealand-s-gateway</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰主要航空枢纽奥克兰机场的首席执行官表示，由于偏远目的地面临低排放燃料短缺的问题，她担心航空业在脱碳方面缺乏进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/aviation-s-emissions-inertia-is-troubling-new-zealand-s-gateway</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱德曼称通货膨胀和就业恐慌加剧国内动乱风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/inflation-and-job-scares-fuel-risk-of-civil-unrest-edelman-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[传播公司爱德曼称，全球通胀恐慌和经济变化会侵蚀就业的担忧加剧了人们认为世界变得越来越不公平的看法，并有可能引发国内骚乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/inflation-and-job-scares-fuel-risk-of-civil-unrest-edelman-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙总理拟禁止非欧盟公民购房</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/spain-s-premier-aims-to-ban-non-eu-citizens-from-buying-homes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯将提议禁止欧盟以外的人在该国购买房屋，这是解决住房短缺问题的更广泛尝试的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/spain-s-premier-aims-to-ban-non-eu-citizens-from-buying-homes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 16:08:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
